headline: Targa Resources (TRGP) PT Lifted to $205 from $191 at RBC Capital
summary: Targa Resources Corp. (NYSE:TRGP) is one of the best high growth stocks. On June 26, RBC Capital lifted its price target from $191 to $205 and maintained an Outperform rating on the stock.
